1. *Odvesti* ću te u školu (I will take you to school).
2. On je *odveo* decu u kupovinu (He took the children to the store).
3. Ona će ga *odvesti* do njegovog doma (She will take him to his house).
4. Oni će je *odvesti* u park (They will take her to the park).
5. Da li ćeš me *odvesti* do stanice? (Will you take me to the station?).
6. Oni će je *odvesti* u šetnju (They will take her for a walk).
7. Ona će njega *odvesti* do bolnice (She will take him to the hospital).
8. *Odvedi* me do njegovog doma (Take me to his house).